IWD NO DBUS
-----------

GOALS

* Get the daemon to function using config files (No iwctl and friends). DONE

* Implement IPC between clients without DBUS. SOON(TM)


NOTE

I am currently in "move fast and possibly break things" mode. Baby steps.


TODO

* Set up CI and build/test each commit automatically.
* Remove all DBUS related code from src/*. DONE
* TBA


BUILDING

    ./configure \
        --prefix=/usr \
        --localstatedir=/var

    make
    make install


SYSTEM-WIDE CONFIG (/etc/iwd/main.conf)

    [General]
    EnableNetworkConfiguration=true
    UseDefaultInterface=true

    [Network]
    NameResolvingService=resolvconf


PER-NETWORK CONFIGS (/var/lib/iwd/ssid.psk)

    [Settings]
    AutoConnect=true

    [Security]
    PreSharedKey=c2b336460f6b294174d2abc08010ed1984208c451e66c22d7be1236ad38cffb7
    Passphrase=2645092660


SSID NAMING

See: IWD.NETWORK(5) (man iwd.network).


HOW DO I FIGURE OUT THE 'PreSharedKey'?

Funny enough, you'll have to use 'wpa_passphrase'.
